STATE EX REL. Cornell MORRIS
v.
STATE of Louisiana NO. 2018-KH-0106 Supreme Court of Louisiana. January 28, 2019

Denied. Relator has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. Morris v. State, 15-1925 (La. 1/9/17), 208 So. 3d 877 .
